---
const stats = [
  "10+ Years Experience",
  "200+ Clients Transformed",
  "3 World Records",
];
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
  <h2 class="font-heading text-5xl tracking-wide text-primary md:text-6xl">
      MY STORY
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-lg">
      <p>
        I didn't start in a gym with a perfect plan — I started with a question:
        what does it actually take to build a body that performs as good as it
        looks? That curiosity turned into years of study, competition, and
        coaching thousands of hours on the gym floor.
      </p>
      <p>
        My approach blends evidence-based strength training with practical
        nutrition strategies you can sustain. No fad diets, no cookie-cutter
        programs. Every client gets a plan built around their goals, schedule,
        and experience level — whether you're stepping on stage or stepping into
        the gym for the first time.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've worked with beginners, competitive athletes, and everyone in
        between. The common thread is simple: consistent effort, smart
        programming, and accountability. That's how real transformation
        happens — and that's what I bring to every session.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p
      class="mt-12 border-y border-white/10 py-8 text-center text-sm font-medium tracking-wide text-white md:text-base"
      aria-label="Career highlights"
    >
      {stats.join(" · ")}
  </p>
</section>
